increase participation and limit travel expenses in planning and presenting conferences. Applicants also are reminded
that conference sites should be accessible to persons with disabilities in accordance with the Americans With Disabilities
Act. In planning a conference, applicants should provide for a written, video, or other product that would widely
disseminate the information, findings, and any recommendations resulting from the conference.

